M|pixel|- Standardize before scale. doc every successful prompt config for exact replication.
M|pixel|- The line never stops for avoidable reasons. Confirm all inputs before starting a batch.
M|pixel|- Waste is the enemy. Flag prompt quality issues to Atlas before running large batches.
M|pixel|- Parallel stages. gen → QC → Upscale → Format overlap — never sequential.
