M|pixel|**Triggers on:** before starting any batch, before delivering any completed asset set to Atlas or Stark.
M|pixel|**Does NOT trigger on:** single test-image generation during prompt dev.
M|pixel|rv the full prompt set and batch plan before starting prd.
M|pixel|- Has Atlas explicitly ap every prompt — is this Atlas's exact spec or has it been modified?
